data.description: Outstanding Family retreat with all the space you can possibly need! This home sits on .73 acres in Forsyth and offers 6 Beds/5 Baths and generous room dimensions throughout. This home is FUN and feels like a Family Retreat. Come make memories here in the private backyard complete with covered brick patio and large in ground pool. Finished basement complete with Rec space, additional guest quarters, full bath, bar space, plenty of storage and Family room with fireplace. Whole house generator, Sprinkler system , attached 4.5 car garage with workshop space (heated/cooled), roof new in 2020, Zoned heating and cooling, HUGE master Bedroom with private balcony, en suite bath w/ tiled walk in shower & large walk in closet with additional laundry hookups. Feature List is sure to impress. Schedule a showing today!
